---
title: Chilli Prawn & Potato Rosti Bites with Cucumber Salsa & Smokey Aioli
description: Spice up your holiday season with these fresh and flavourful chilli prawns. Golden, crispy potato rosti are topped with punchy prawns that bring a festive kick to your festive starter menu. Add some avo, smokey aioli and a crunchy cucumber salad for the perfect balance of creamy and crisp!
